name: Behemoth
description:
''What a mighty big creature is the Behemoth, my master... I remember he carries us to help him with creating mayhem. Oh... I still remember how great it feels, while master Behemoth uses its mighty trunk to behead a worthless mortal... So fun... I miss my master, hope he returns when the great day comes!''

A servant demon of Behemoth, location unknown.
